page.title: 02Andrea from Moulton Seas End
page.content: I get up and go out of my bedroom and go down stairs. I wash myself.I have my breakfast. I sometimes have branflakes or cornflakes. Then I go to the shop to get my dinner and pack it up. Then I get in my grandad's car. I set off for school about twenty five to nine and arrive at ten to nine .I live about two miles from Holbeach Bank. We have an assembly. We have brain busters.Then we have maths and English.We go out to play 10.30 and 12.30. I have my Dinner about 12.00. I have a drink, apple flavour, and crisps and a chocolate biscuit. When I get home I have my tea and go out to play with my friends and the next morning I do it all over again.
